OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FITV Border has sat down with all the
OL,8,Fmain political party leaders during
OL,9,Fthe Holyrood election campaign.
OL,11,FThe final interview was with Gillian
OL,12,FMackay and Ross Greer of the Scottish
OL,13,FGreens. Here are three things we
OL,14,Flearned.
OL,16,FThey're desperate for a South Scotland
OL,17,Fseat
OL,19,FIn 2021, the Scottish Greens missed
OL,20,Fout on returning an MSP for our region
OL,21,Fby just 115 votes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FThat stung them, not least because
OL,8,Fthey blamed the result on a far-right
OL,9,Fparty called Independent Green Voice,
OL,10,Fwho won 1,690 votes, being on the
OL,11,Fballot paper.
OL,13,FNow, both Ms Mackay and Mr Greer say
OL,14,Fthey are "really confident" of picking
OL,15,Fup representation in the south.
OL,17,F"Like across the country, many folk
OL,18,Fare looking for a wee bit of change
OL,19,Fand something different and something
OL,20,Fhopeful to be able to put their cross
OL,21,Fbeside," said Ms Mackay.
OL,26,@vD@JOUvD@[O]yD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FMr Greer added: "Especially when you
OL,8,Fsee the number of people that we're
OL,9,Fspeaking to, on the regional, the
OL,10,Fpeach ballot, it's probably going to
OL,11,Fbe between the Greens and Reform for
OL,12,Fthe final seat on a lot of these
OL,13,Fregional lists.
OL,15,F"For a lot of people that's a real
OL,16,Fmotivator, particularly with how
OL,17,FReform have behaved, they at that
OL,18,Fpoint become pretty enthusiastic about
OL,19,Fvoting for the Greens to vote for
OL,20,Fsomething not just against."
OL,26,@oD@QOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FThe Greens' strategy, like many other
OL,8,Fparties, is focused on winning seats
OL,9,Fon the regional list.
OL,11,FThe party is only standing candidates
OL,12,Fin six first past the post
OL,13,Fconstituencies and their co-leaders
OL,14,Fare not amongst them.
OL,16,FSo who are they voting for on that
OL,17,Fballot paper? Ms Mackay said she "will
OL,18,Fmake up my mind on polling day" while
OL,19,FMr Greer said he had a "pretty good
OL,20,Fidea" who he would back but refused to
OL,21,Freveal the lucky candidate.
OL,26,@yD@bOUzD@_O]{D@XOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FThey LOVE buses ` but do they have a
OL,8,Fcredible plan to improve services?
OL,10,FA flagship Green policy is to make bus
OL,11,Ftravel free for everyone and bring in
OL,12,Fminimum levels of service in rural
OL,13,Fareas.
OL,15,FThis is something that will strike a
OL,16,Fchord with people in Dumfries and
OL,17,FGalloway in particular given the axing
OL,18,Fof routes across the council area.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FBut how do you pay for that?
OL,8,FEspecially when the plan involves more
OL,9,Froutes being established and is costed
OL,10,Fat around #275 million, which is only
OL,11,Faround #8.6 million for each council.
OL,13,FMr Greer said: "That's why we're
OL,14,Fproposing full public ownership of the
OL,15,Fbuses. Privatisation for 40 years
OL,16,Fhasn't worked.
OL,18,F"The companies are only interested in
OL,19,Fprofitable routes. And that it is
OL,20,Fpublicly funded out of general
OL,21,Ftaxation.
OL,26,@uD@POUzD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,F"We have seen the success of free bus
OL,8,Ftravel for young people. Other
OL,9,Fcountries do universal free bus
OL,10,Ftravel, Malta, Luxembourg, parts of
OL,11,FAustralia are bringing it in now
OL,12,Fbecause of Trump's fuel crisis."
OL,14,FQuestions remain about whether the
OL,15,Fplans add up
OL,17,FThis dovetails neatly into one of the
OL,18,Fbig questions that still hangs over
OL,19,Fthe Scottish Greens: are they just a
OL,20,Fparty offering shiny things with no
OL,21,Frealistic way of paying for them?
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
