PN,35908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies think-
OL,8,Ftank said of the party's manifesto
OL,9,Fthat "increases in taxes would
OL,10,Fprobably have to be even larger than
OL,11,Fsuggested, or cuts made to other day-
OL,12,Fto-day spending that the Scottish
OL,13,FGreens deem lower priority" to fulfil
OL,14,Fits spending pledges.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, the Fraser of Allander
OL,17,Feconomic institute said the prospectus
OL,18,Fhad the "most extensive tax section of
OL,19,Fany manifesto so far, but detail on
OL,20,Fcostings and delivery is largely
OL,21,Fabsent".
OL,26,@qD@FOUuD@[O]zD@IOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FMr Greer said that analysis didn't
OL,8,Ftake into account planned cuts through
OL,9,Fscrapping standardised testing in
OL,10,Fschools (#6 million) and the small
OL,11,Fbusiness bonus (#250 million), which
OL,12,Fthey say is tapped into by "loads of
OL,13,Freally big businesses".
OL,15,FThat's not enough to pay for just the
OL,16,Fbus policy but Ms Mackay is insistent
OL,17,Fthe money is out there.
OL,26,@tD@\OUuD@VO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FShe said: "I think what we need to
OL,8,Ffocus on is actually how we fund them
OL,9,Fand how we deliver them. The top 2% in
OL,10,FScotland has as much wealth as 50% of
OL,11,Fthe rest of the population.
OL,13,F"There's not a lack of money out there
OL,14,Fat the moment.
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,F"We haven't pulled the right levers
OL,8,Fyet to be able to have that money to
OL,9,Fbe able to spend on these upgrades
OL,10,Fthat we want, making sure that
OL,11,Fcommunities have good services, that
OL,12,Fthey are sustainable and well funded,
OL,13,Fthat we bring more powers forward for
OL,14,Flocal authorities to be able to raise
OL,15,Ftheir own money and spend it locally."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FThe IFS also said the Greens' plans
OL,8,Fwould probably mean tax increases
OL,9,Fwould have to be "larger than
OL,10,Fexpected" and would "cement Scotland's
OL,11,Fposition as the highest taxed part of
OL,12,Fthe UK".
OL,14,FSo does this risk driving away people
OL,15,Fon Scotland's median salary of just
OL,16,Fover #40,000 over the border to
OL,17,FEngland for lower rates?
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@IO]rD@UOUtD@GO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,FBoth leaders pointed out that more
OL,8,Fhigher income taxpayers in Scotland
OL,9,Fnow than 10 years ago to say mass
OL,10,Fexodus has not happened.
OL,12,FMr Greer said: "For someone earning
OL,13,F#40,000 we've no plans to increase
OL,14,Fincome tax. Our focus is on taxing the
OL,15,Fwealth of the genuine super rich.
OL,26,@tD@POU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1778328668
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CGillian Mackay and Ross Greer leaders
OL,5,Cinterview
OL,7,F"If you are earning #40,000 and you're
OL,8,Fliving in Gatehouse of Fleet or
OL,9,Fsomething, you want to move a few
OL,10,Fmiles south you then lose the free bus
OL,11,Ftravel that if you're young or your
OL,12,Fchildren are young that they get.
OL,14,F"Your children will not get free
OL,15,Funiversity tuition, you won't get free
OL,16,Fsocial care, free prescriptions, etc.
OL,17,FSo there's an element of social
OL,18,Fsolidarity here."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
